## Frontend (Next.js) - `frontend` folder

### Installed Packages
- `tailwindcss@3.4.17`, `postcss`, `autoprefixer`: Utility styling. Initialize with:
```bash
npx tailwindcss init -p
```
- `shadcn/ui`: Components styled with Tailwind. Initialize with:
```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```
Add components:
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component>
```
Example: `npx shadcn@latest add toast`

### Creation
```bash
npx create-next-app@latest sistema_gente
```

